Kate Fitzgerald https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kate_Fitzgerald 0 Kate Fitzgerald is a British television actress from Liverpool. She best known for playing Doreen Corkhill for five years in defunct soap opera Brookside (1985–89), Nancy Tinker in Coronation Street, and Loretta Chase in Benidorm.
